result.name: New Paris Vietnam Restaurant

reviews.text:
New Paris Vietnam restaurant located on the 5/F of Island Beverley, although their decorations are old, but their food is nice and decent.
The taste of their food is not great, but it's decent.  And as this is not a popular restaurant, you don't have to wait for any table even during lunch peak hours

Based on only one visit, it's possibly worst Vietnamese restaurant I've ever been to. Pho bore no resemblance to any other, vegetable water. More like super cheap Chinese restaurant with added sauces. Will not waste my money there again.
Had soup of the day, lemongrass pork chop, stir fried vegetables and Vietnamese summer roll. All were good and price were really reasonable.

An affordable Vietnam Cuisine small restaurant run by a honest and diligent owner.  Place is clean and food is generally good.  Should not expect very high quality with a low price.  Quantity is well enough to make you feel stuffed.
The noodles is not even Pho style and the soup base is not even great. This is not a Vietnamese cuisine. Not worth going

result.adr_address: 香港銅鑼灣記利佐治街金堡中心
result.formatted_address: 香港銅鑼灣記利佐治街金堡中心
result.name: 新巴黎越南餐廳

reviews.text:
原來轉左手，唔怪得食物質素味道差到咁誇張仲要勁少選擇，唔知係侍應定老闆同我地講剛剛轉手會慢慢加番多啲野食！
其實依間野我係由本身起灣仔軒尼詩道食到依家起銅鑼灣，最少食左十四年以上，又一間好食又抵食嘅餐廳成左回憶！
以前銅鑼灣做野會黎lunch，原來舊老闆已經退左休，餐牌都轉晒....選擇都變得好少....平心而論味道合格既，香茅豬扒唔會死實、雞翼ok，小食春卷都可以...但就完全唔係以往既味道...可以當係一間新餐廳咁...

New Paris Vietnam restaurant located on the 5/F of Island Beverley, although their decorations are old, but their food is nice and decent.
The taste of their food is not great, but it's decent.  And as this is not a popular restaurant, you don't have to wait for any table even during lunch peak hours
轉了新menu, 價錢合理的好選擇

去這間餐廳吃晚餐，很好吃! 我吃炒牛河，和香茅豬扒飯。都很有水準!
牛油雞翼也很好
千萬別去旁邊的易牙台式料理。很伏！

result.name: Saigon Saigon

reviews.text:
Horrible! I ordered saigoon cold vermicelli, noodles were not even half cooked, too hard to chew.
Also ordered beef spicy cubes, and they were completely raw inside, I love sashimi, but I didn't see that coming and almost vomit, disgusting!
It was horrible we ordered basic Pho for my wife and myself and it was so bad.. I really don't like to say bad for any restaurant but this was definitely waste of money.

Fantastic food, great service.
Highly recommended.

Eaten Vietnamese food practically most of my life. Location is on the 7th floor and the elevator takes forever. The beef pho was not  bad but definitely could be better. One bowl was not enough for me. Skip on the baht mi pate. Mostly bread and not enough substance.
Finally an authentic Vietnamese Pho and Banh Mi joint!!!  Must try
